race.comment: DAPPER CHAP (2) goes very well this trip starting eight times for three wins and four minors. Hit the frame latest (29.61) when third at Sandown in a Grade 5. Looks a leading chance on best. ASTON COUNTACH (4) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (29.85) last time out at Sandown. Has never been out of the money in five starts this distance. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Bold showing expected. ASTON PRATT (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 30.01 beating Jetstream Icon. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expecting another bold showing. HEAD FOR HOME (7) can fill a top-three spot.
